      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-tit-pgm-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su flag di visualizzazione titolo          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-sts-vis-tit    not  = spaces
                     move  spaces         to   w-cnt-sts-vis-tit
                     go to vis-tit-pgm-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Erase video                                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "ER"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Trattini a linea 01                             *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      01                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      all   "="            to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
